{"tid":1421888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗狗記者會學習重點","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:48:28.000Z","uid":287903,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e56b0796a8e54d9c24423af062875cb9018efe","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"見到班狗開記者會，有幾樣野可以借鑑，等民間記者會可以做得更好。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 重覆重點</span><br />\n不斷重覆自己論點，無論人地點問元朗721，都係重覆佢地所謂「已掌握」既資料<br />\n當然唔係叫大家避答記者問題，但如果唔識答，可以學呢招。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 適時偷換概念</span><br />\n被人質疑警員操守同失控，嘗試Spin去警員好慘，而從來無回應黑警有無失控，側面回應話定時會有情緒支援<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 有道歉</span><br />\n個大sir好識做戲，佢扮得好humble，亦願意向受傷道歉，但佢講明道歉背後，是因為出現「誤會」，佢地並無錯。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">歡迎大家集思廣益，學習對方長處再以此攻之。要記住，我地既觀眾係市民大眾，要講一D大家都易理解同易接受既說話。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"31c3797d38ddd318cd1e59263d67597fb8c44a8d","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:13:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e4afabb068c0e0a4edcb7ea4cf2c81160e4e927","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bd0799bc1b4773adb718fa4489bfa307de2db16","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90d8a0ff9887f74c857e523622edd443104e29d8","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b486e3070bdfe41208ab20abb9fc26db39d5a873","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"957cb9482ead5bd40535fb392ef49dc1ec23b8f9","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:15:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f022f38e0ea0f71e36ed604fdd23567d79c5801","tid":1421888,"uid":287903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB